<div id="s1362" data-link-target="s1362" data-id="section/1362" class="section article-list level1 article-body"><p class="content">The Bangladesh Inland Water Transport Corporation Order, 1972 (P.O. No. 28 of 1972)</p></div><!--Section: section/1363, type: body-->
