<div id="s1371" data-link-target="s1371" data-id="section/1371" class="section article-list level1 article-body"><p class="content">The Bangladesh Government Hats and Bazars (Management) Order, 1972 (P.O. No. 73 of 1972)</p></div><!--Section: section/1372, type: body-->
<div id="s1372" data-link-target="s1372" data-id="section/1372" class="section article-list level1 article-body"><p class="content">The Bangladesh Government and Semi-autonomous Organisations (Regulation of Salary of Employees) Order, 1972 (P.O. No. 79 of 1972)</p></div><!--Section: section/1373, type: body-->
